// Canonical ambient declarations for Tish globals, namespaces, and timers.
//
// LSP "Go to definition" for built-ins is driven by lines of the form:
//   // @tish-source <symbol> <path-from-repo-root> <1-based-line>
//
// Symbols may be dotted (`console.log`, `Math.abs`). Paths are relative to the
// `tishlang/tish` repository root (same layout as `tish_eval`, `tish_ui`, etc.).

// --- @tish-source anchors (keep in sync with interpreter / runtime) ---

